commit 05ebde239e74acc0845ad761448f7ae7039291e5
Author: Martin Lambers <marlam@marlam.de>
Date:   2018-01-15 14:53:36 +0100

    Disable handling of StereoscopicSkip metadata tag (used by 3dtv.at)
    
    The reason is that seeking in WMV files is notoriously unreliable with FFmpeg.
    
    It is better to see the 3dtv.at advertisement in the skip section than to miss
    the correct beginning of the content due to seeking failures.

 src/media_input.cpp | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

commit 4863bf80ab9a2091456bb9c833f90cd66dfbca12
Author: Martin Lambers <marlam@marlam.de>
Date:   2018-01-15 14:52:59 +0100

    Fix handling of StereoscopicSkip metadata tag (used by 3dtv.at)

 src/media_input.cpp | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

