Author: Martin Lambers <marlam@marlam.de>
Date:   2012-09-25 21:34:56 +0200

    Require only GLSL version 1.10.
    
    Version 1.10 is specified with OpenGL 2.0; version 1.20 is specified with
    OpenGL 2.1. We only need 1.10.

