Date:   2010-11-07 11:03:34 +0100

    Allow building with older glew versions.
    
    Avoid GL_GEOMETRY_SHADER and GL_GEOMETRY_SHADER_ARB, and use
    GL_GEOMETRY_SHADER_EXT instead, which has the same value.

